      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ParquetByteInspector
      The ParquetByteInspector can inspect both ByteWritables and IntWritables into bytes.
      class  ParquetShortInspector
      The ParquetShortInspector can inspect both ShortWritables and IntWritables into shorts.
      class  ParquetStringInspector
      The ParquetStringInspector inspects a BytesWritable, TimestampWritableV2, HiveDecimalWritable, DoubleWritable, FloatWritable, LongWritable, IntWritable, and BooleanWritable to give a Text or String.
